OL,5, Roger Corman, who directed a series of 
OL,6, cult films including 1960's The Little 
OL,7, Shop of Horrors, has died aged 98.     
OL,9,FHis family told industry publication   
OL,10,FVariety that he died on Thursday at his
OL,11,Fhome in Santa Monica, California.      
OL,13,F"His films were revolutionary and      
OL,14,Ficonoclastic, and captured the spirit  
OL,15,Fof an age," their statement said.      
OL,17,FJack Nicholson and Robert De Niro are  
OL,18,Famong the actors he helped develop.    
OL,19,FDirectors James Cameron and Martin     
OL,20,FScorsese cut their teeth on his films. 
